cb1-b59d-4bc2-b81c-c078b44d9603" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R5db2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-j50d06"><div data-rid="f984ff26-c572-4110-89ca-41a5a32a06fd" class="r-zett81 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Will I wake up groggy in the morning?</p></span></div><div data-rid="1bedda76-1235-4c09-9cc8-e295acf3f1bb" class="r-1no5irx" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-uwjrmq" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R5db2:"><div data-rid="fbfbfe0d-37c1-4c18-ad0d-a274c4b3ccb4" class="r-ph5a8j"><div data-rid="57b4d9b7-c05a-45e7-98c1-c3d4a0eab346" class="r-147a79t alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>No, and this is the #1 reason people switch to Rejuvia. We use a low 2mg dose of melatonin (most gummies pack 5-10mg, which is what causes the morning hangover) paired with 12 natural sleep herbs that calm your mind without knocking you out cold. You'll wake up rested, not foggy.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="498e936f-edef-43ba-8b4b-8b94558917fe" class="r-14ciimh" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="bb721166-01cf-4ac3-961e-a61b12c0020e" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R7db2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1bkyvbt"><div data-rid="db57a562-3cc1-4b8b-aabf-4e1d6cbaecf2" class="r-1jtkksp alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>How fast will I feel Rejuvia working?</p></span></div><div data-rid="5d4f7be5-e84c-498e-9b46-7753d08aaa25" class="r-y4fn6w" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-d2hqhb" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R7db2:"><div data-rid="a014bf20-0907-40eb-933f-1912a07f123e" class="r-kj7mea"><div data-rid="612c35b6-6e8d-4218-a1d8-89e2c0f4ae02" class="r-3st2if alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Most people feel it the first or second night. Because the spray absorbs under your tongue, it skips your stomach completely and gets to work in about 10-15 minutes instead of the 60-90 minutes pills and gummies take. That said, if you've been dealing with bad sleep for years, give it a full 7-10 nights of consistent use. The ingredients build on each other and the deeper, full-night sleep typically kicks in by the end of week one.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="143c4ead-0764-419d-8b37-091fa0e0a848" class="r-13nnhc3" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="21cbd366-13cb-47e7-8dd6-3b729fbe9a36" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R9db2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-x4z9o8"><div data-rid="38273a2b-c634-47b0-a785-355c7c306dbd" class="r-7jp9oz alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Is Rejuvia habit-forming? Will I become dependent on it?</p></span></div><div data-rid="3d8cb644-c786-4dc1-bdc1-8ae5bb338fd6" class="r-e1lb99" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1l2ykn2" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R9db2:"><div data-rid="4ac89594-a649-4556-96f8-1c4fffb5cdb2" class="r-skf4oq"><div data-rid="18eb54eb-9f64-4136-8934-b45de58bcee1" class="r-1h714se alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Not at all. Rejuvia is non-habit-forming, and you can use it every night or only when you need it. Most of our customers use it nightly as part of their wind-down routine because they love how they feel, not because they have to. Plenty of customers also use it 3-4 nights a week or only when travel and stress throw off their sleep.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="1ef4d1fa-6be2-4552-b1c0-f50934e5334e" class="r-m3u4zr" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="8b6590d2-20de-4632-af58-158e2e315221" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rbdb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-w9ulpr"><div data-rid="5aaefecd-38d4-473b-8995-4f68076c9fe5" class="r-1w5dexv alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What are the ingredients in Rejuvia?</p></span></div><div data-rid="082b52ff-773b-45fa-82b1-fb2f6a74a098" class="r-f2irxm" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-r1jfyr" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rbdb2:"><div data-rid="0fa3e14a-28f7-44df-868e-21c79aa3c7e9" class="r-ie703m"><div data-rid="7ad2c87d-fe9d-49bc-ad7c-bcd0893bb9d0" class="r-1v75q18 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Rejuvia has 13 all-natural ingredients working together: a low 2mg of melatonin, plus 5-HTP, valerian root, passionflower, chamomile, lemon balm, skullcap, magnolia bark, hops, cramp bark, ginkgo biloba, peppermint, and feverfew. That's why it works on falling asleep, staying asleep, and waking up refreshed instead of just one of the three.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="2869a2cd-83c5-4dd0-80ce-f1f1b737c30a" class="r-u5unwo" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="34b217f2-68b4-4edd-bfa1-9b18620c1164" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rddb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-10f5ugr"><div data-rid="6963c35c-63d9-4a3b-98b8-5fc73d421349" class="r-txrj54 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What flavor is Rejuvia?</p></span></div><div data-rid="6523fbc1-fdc2-472b-85ec-b391b46760e1" class="r-11yopa7" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1bz1asy" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rddb2:"><div data-rid="ecddae41-bc66-44e6-a385-60d76f1b8cb9" class="r-1vjqkfh"><div data-rid="8f0e36b6-af88-4507-842c-c1b13d0846d1" class="r-1ctv2ya alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Rejuvia oral sprays have a refreshing, all-natural mint flavoring. It's noticeable and refreshing but mild — if you don't love mint, it's not overpowering.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="c25b3892-ba52-445b-bfd9-dd9252255e76" class="r-1m68o8y" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="ba83e8fd-b827-4917-b4f7-0116226ae023" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rfdb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1789sd"><div data-rid="89f61faf-3b73-4a83-9623-6f10ca077bec" class="r-1i82itv alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Is this a subscription?</p></span></div><div data-rid="60160318-388e-4628-ab43-74db6661f1a9" class="r-15r8mez" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-t6cad3" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rfdb2:"><div data-rid="b5e339e3-a67c-4502-a253-dab6c7ce410c" class="r-1f8h0y8"><div data-rid="ee1fec7c-5f17-400f-bfde-2a50d71643cb" class="r-1q779rq alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Nope. This is a one-time purchase, no subscription, no auto-billing, no strings attached. You pay once, we ship it, and that's it. If you love it and want to set up automatic refills later to save more, you can do that from our main product page anytime.</p><p><br></p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="5728daec-c248-42cf-8ee0-43eeb2bed168" class="r-49h4g6" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="febfd44b-56ba-4afa-b2ce-fcb62401ce51" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rhdb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1k8tjsv"><div data-rid="a1a3b234-a0e4-4493-9828-1288ac87c24a" class="r-14tkrmn alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>How long does one bottle last and when will my order arrive?</p></span></div><div data-rid="2370eb35-7c7b-4067-89ef-6095fd370f45" class="r-i0kuuw" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1m1vr37" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rhdb2:"><div data-rid="e822de75-9272-4912-8e37-df53f22e5e2d" class="r-1x6xd8"><div data-rid="91821073-9d41-4867-8014-f7a7d6d5e6d4" class="r-1fmthgy alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Each bottle has 240 sprays, which lasts about 30-35 nights at the recommended 6-8 sprays per night. We ship every order within 24 hours and most orders arrive within 2-3 business days.</p></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="6ea95df2-6d2d-48e4-9872-376b69cd86e4" class="r-1vkvo0m" data-alchemy-prerendered-component-id="6ea95df2-6d2d-48e4-9872-376b69cd86e4">{%- comment -%}replo-liquid-chunk-begin{%- endcomment -%}<div style="width:100%;height:100%" data-alchemy-prerendered-placeholder="true">{% section 'page-cta-v2' %}</div>{%- comment -%}replo-liquid-chunk-end{%- endcomment -%}</div></div></div></div><style id="replo-fonts-HelveticaNeueLTPro-Bd">
